				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$T_2^ \ast$$\end{document} is 150 ms. In natural photosynthetic complexes, the energy transfer is completed within 50 ps. For the scaling factor in our proposal, it corresponds to 7.5 ms, which is smaller than T2*\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
